title: Candy Making for Kids - EPUB - WD
description:
Year: 2012 
ISBN: 142363022X 
Language: English 
Pages: 64 pages 
Format: EPUB 

Another creative favorite from the author of Push-up Pops and Pizzazzerie.com

Candy Making for Kids is a creative and fun book full of easyto-follow candy recipes for kids. 

From traditional favorites such as toffee and fudge to whimsical creations such as candy caterpillars and candy play-dough, kids of all ages will absolutely love these delicious and cute treats. 

Perfect for childrens parties, holiday parties, packaging up for friends, or simply enjoying at home, these recipe ideas are sure to become a family favorite!
